item.title: The Undertones - Teenage Kicks
item.description:
Ukulele play along Teenage Kicks - The Undertones
Using the chords: C Cmaj7 F G Am
Suggested Strum Patterns: D DU U DU or a more complicated D DU D DU UDU DU DU
The audio has been slightly altered to suit a better key for the ukulele.
This video is meant for educational purposes.
No copyright infringement intended
